'''Denuvo防篡改'''（{{lang-en|Denuvo Anti-Tamper}}）或'''Denuvo'''，是由[[奥地利|奥地利]]Denuvo软件解决方案股份有限公司（Denuvo Software Solutions GmbH）开发的一种[[防篡改|防篡改]]技术。该公司通过[[索尼数字音频光盘公司|索尼数字音频光盘公司]]的[[管理层收购|管理层收购]]（MBO）而组成。2018年1月，'''Denuvo'''被{{nl-link|Irdeto}}收购<ref>[http://www.gamelook.com.cn/2018/01/319066 Denuvo被安全大厂收购：联手让破解游戏消失] {{Wayback|url=http://www.gamelook.com.cn/2018/01/319066 |date=20190924234144 }}.GAMELOOK.</ref>。

Denuvo声称这项技术不是一个[[数字版权管理|数字版权管理]]（DRM）的解决方案，因为它旨在保护现有的DRM解决方案，如[[Origin_(电子游戏平台)|Origin]]联机访问和[[Steam|Steam]]许可管理制度<ref name="Denuvo">{{cite web|url=http://www.denuvo.com/|title=Denuvo|website=www.denuvo.com|publisher=Denuvo Software Solutions GmbH|accessdate=2014-11-30|archive-date=2014-12-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20141202080608/http://www.denuvo.com/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==技术==
早期报道认为Denuvo防篡改“连续对自身进行加密和解密，所以它是不可能被破解的。”<ref name="ASidCast" /> Denuvo软件解决方案指出该技术“不对存储介质上的任何数据进行连续加密和解密。因为这样做对安全和性能方面并无益处。”该公司没有透露Denuvo防篡改的工作方式<ref name="Denuvo" />。2014年12月1日，[[3DMGAME|3DM]]技术组声称已破解Denuvo防篡改，并发布了使用Denuvo保护的[[艺电|EA]] [[Origin_(电子游戏平台)|Origin]]联机访问DRM的电子游戏《[[龙腾世纪：审判|龙腾世纪：审判]]》的破解演示视频<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.3dmgame.com/news/201412/3406040.html|title = 《龙腾世纪：审判》告破 DenuvoDRM并非无懈可击|accessdate = 2015-02-06|author = [[宿菲菲|宿菲菲]]|date = 2014-12-01|publisher = [[3DMGAME|3DMGAME]]|archive-date = 2015-02-16|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150216235258/http://www.3dmgame.com/news/201412/3406040.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Eurogamer">{{cite web|last1=Purchese|first1=Robert|title=Don't call it DRM: what's Denuvo Anti-Tamper?|url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-12-19-denuvo-anti-tamper-drm|website=Eurogamer|publisher=Eurogamer|accessdate=2016-02-06|archive-date=2016-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160211132537/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2014-12-19-denuvo-anti-tamper-drm|dead-url=no}}</ref>，破解花费了15天，这对PC游戏来说并不寻常<ref name="Eurogamer" />。3DM技术人员称该技术涉及“64位加密”，每个已安装的系统的特定硬件都需要唯一的加密密钥<ref>{{Cite web|title = Denuvo DRM has been cracked - PC Invasion|url = http://www.pcinvasion.com/denuvo-drm-has-been-cracked|accessdate = 2015-09-04|archive-date = 2015-10-17|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20151017204843/http://www.pcinvasion.com/denuvo-drm-has-been-cracked|dead-url = no}}</ref>。在被问及该技术的发展时，Denuvo承认“每一个受保护的游戏最终都会被破解。”<ref name="Eurogamer" /> [[Ars_Technica|Ars Technica]]指出主流游戏发布后30天内是其最重要的销售时期，如果Denuvo加密意味着一个游戏会在较长时间后被攻破，那么发行商会认为它是成功的<ref>{{cite news|last1=Orland|first1=Kyle|title=Major piracy group warns games may be crack-proof in two years|url=http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2016/01/major-piracy-groups-warns-games-may-be-crack-proof-in-two-years/|accessdate=2016-01-07|work=Ars Technica|date=2016-01-07|archive-date=2016-01-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160108070349/http://arstechnica.com/gaming/2016/01/major-piracy-groups-warns-games-may-be-crack-proof-in-two-years/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2016年1月，3DM站长[[宿菲菲|宿菲菲]]发文表示受Denuvo保护的《[[正当防卫3|正当防卫3]]》破解到跨处理器时，由于难度太大 ，几乎放弃<ref name="polygon">{{cite web | url=http://www.polygon.com/2016/1/9/10741274/just-cause-3-crack-pc-3gm-denuvo | title=Piracy group nearly gives up on cracking Just Cause 3, warns of bleak future | publisher=www.polygon.com | date=2016-01-09 | accessdate=2016-01-17 | author=Owen S. Good | archive-date=2016-01-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160119134155/http://www.polygon.com/2016/1/9/10741274/just-cause-3-crack-pc-3gm-denuvo | dead-url=no }}</ref>。她还称按照目前的加密技术趋势发展，两年后PC游戏将无法破解<ref name="polygon" /><ref name="eurogamer_tide">{{cite web | url=http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-01-08-denuvo-game-crack-success | title=Finally, tide turns in war with PC game crackers | publisher=www.eurogamer.net | date=2016-01-08 | accessdate=2016-01-18 | author=Robert Purchese | archive-date=2016-01-19 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160119193146/http://www.eurogamer.net/articles/2016-01-08-denuvo-game-crack-success | dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url = http://weibo.com/1957183442/Dbrn9mzpX|title = 宿菲菲对《正当防卫3》破解进度的回应|accessdate = 2016-02-06|author = 宿菲菲|date = 2016-01-03|publisher = |archive-date = 2019-09-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190924234141/https://passport.weibo.com/visitor/visitor?entry=miniblog&a=enter&url=https%3A%2F%2Fweibo.com%2F1957183442%2FDbrn9mzpX&domain=.weibo.com&ua=php-sso_sdk_client-0.6.28&_rand=1569368500.8416|dead-url = no}}</ref>。 Denuvo的托马斯·戈贝尔（Thomas Goebl）认为这种技术的存在会使一些主机独占的游戏发布PC版本<ref name="eurogamer_tide" />。2月，受《[[三国志13|三国志13]]》破解风波的影响<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://www.3dmgame.com/news/201602/3546055.html|title = 日本光荣公司警告3DM 《三国志13》将无免费下载|accessdate = 2016-02-06|author = |date = 2016-02-02|publisher = 3DMGAME|deadurl = yes|archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160204221629/http://www.3dmgame.com/news/201602/3546055.html|archivedate = 2016-02-04}}</ref>，3DM决定停止一切对Denuvo加密的继续研究<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://weibo.com/1957183442/DgpoLCkCu|title = 宿菲菲发文表示停止一切对Denuvo加密的继续研究|accessdate = 2016-02-06|author = 宿菲菲|date = 2016-02-05|publisher =}}</ref>。几天后，宿菲菲再次发文称3DM近期会公布最新Denuvo加密的解决方案，包括《FIFA 16》、《正当防卫3》、《古墓奇兵：崛起》，并表示“目前我们还没有被难住”<ref>{{Cite web|url = http://mt.sohu.com/20160208/n437124893.shtml|title = 外媒称3DM因技术难题暂停破解 创始人回应|accessdate = 2016-02-14|author = |date = 2016-02-08|publisher = [[搜狐|搜狐]]|archive-date = 2016-02-22|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160222070649/http://mt.sohu.com/20160208/n437124893.shtml|dead-url = no}}</ref>。2016年8月初，有报道称《[[毁灭战士_(2016年游戏)|毁灭战士]]》的Denuvo保护已被绕过<ref>{{cite web|last1=Papadopoulos|first1=John|title=Denuvo has been defeated, first working crack for DOOM is now available {{!}} DSOGaming {{!}} The Dark Side Of Gaming|url=http://www.dsogaming.com/news/denuvo-has-been-defeated-first-doom-crack-is-now-available/|website=DSOGaming|accessdate=2016-08-06|archive-date=2016-08-05|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160805210838/http://www.dsogaming.com/news/denuvo-has-been-defeated-first-doom-crack-is-now-available/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，其他游戏的破解会在随后几天放出<ref>{{cite web|last1=Papadopoulos|first1=John|title=Just Cause 3, Rise of the Tomb Raider & Inside have been cracked/bypassed {{!}} DSOGaming {{!}} The Dark Side Of Gaming|url=http://www.dsogaming.com/news/just-cause-3-rise-of-the-tomb-raider-inside-have-been-crackedbypassed/|website=DSOGaming|accessdate=2016-08-07|archive-date=2016-08-08|archive-url=https://archive.is/20160808040945/http://www.dsogaming.com/news/just-cause-3-rise-of-the-tomb-raider-inside-have-been-crackedbypassed/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。尽管破解组第一次发布后这些漏洞已被修复，但后来《古墓奇兵：崛起》、《[[Inside_(游戏)|Inside]]》和《毁灭战士》接连被破解小组CONSPIR4CY（CPY）攻破<ref>{{cite web|title=Denuvo Properly Cracked, "Rise of the Tomb Raider" First Victim - TorrentFreak|url=https://torrentfreak.com/denuvo-properly-cracked-rise-of-the-tomb-raider-first-victim-160809/|website=TorrentFreak|accessdate=2016-08-09|date=2016-08-09|archive-date=2016-08-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160809171154/https://torrentfreak.com/denuvo-properly-cracked-rise-of-the-tomb-raider-first-victim-160809/|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。[[Playdead|Playdead]]后来更新移除了《Inside》的Denuvo加密<ref name="InsideRemoval">{{cite web|url=http://steamcommunity.com/games/304430/announcements/detail/510426185159035029|title=INSIDE patch notes 2016/11/23|date=2016-11-23|access-date=2017-02-08|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211080952/http://steamcommunity.com/games/304430/announcements/detail/510426185159035029|dead-url=no}}</ref>。[[id_Software|id Software]]同样也在2016年12月通过补丁的形式移除了《毁灭战士》的Denuvo加密<ref name="DoomRemoval">{{cite web|url=https://torrentfreak.com/denuvo-removed-from-doom-after-game-gets-cracked-161208/|title=Denuvo Removed From Doom After Game Gets Cracked|date=2016-12-09|access-date=2017-02-08|archive-date=2017-02-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170211155130/https://torrentfreak.com/denuvo-removed-from-doom-after-game-gets-cracked-161208/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年1月29日，《[[惡靈古堡7|生化危机7]]》在发售5天后遭CPY破解，成为最快被破解的使用最新Denuvo技术的游戏<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.dsogaming.com/news/resident-evil-7-latest-version-of-the-denuvo-anti-tamper-tech-has-been-cracked-in-less-than-five-days/|title=Resident Evil 7 – Latest version of the Denuvo anti-tamper tech cracked in less than five days|accessdate=2017-01-30|archive-date=2017-01-30|archive-url=https://archive.is/20170130091003/http://www.dsogaming.com/news/resident-evil-7-latest-version-of-the-denuvo-anti-tamper-tech-has-been-cracked-in-less-than-five-days/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
2017年5月7日，俄罗斯黑客组织破解了使用Denuvo最新版本的游戏《[[尼爾：自動人形|尼爾：自動人形]]》和《[[狙擊之王：幽灵战士3|狙擊之王：幽灵战士3]]》，之后又陆续破解多款使用Denuvo的游戏<ref name="tekken7">{{cite web|url=https://www.xrel.to/p2p/168820-Tekken7-v1-0-Crack-V3-by-BALDMAN/nfo.html|title=Tekken7.v1.0.Crack.V3.by.BALDMAN|author=|website=|date=|publisher=www.xrel.to|accessdate=2017-06-06|archive-date=2019-02-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190215223356/https://www.xrel.to/p2p/168820-Tekken7-v1-0-Crack-V3-by-BALDMAN/nfo.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2017年6月6日，匿名黑客组织STEAMPUNKS攻破《[[冤罪殺機2|冤罪殺機2]]》<ref name="STEAMPUNKS Keygen">{{cite web|url=https://geektimes.ru/post/289965/|title=Keygen information for hacking game Dishonored 2 (Attention, article is written in Russian language!).|author=|website=|date=|publisher=|accessdate=2017-06-11|archive-date=2017-06-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170610224147/https://geektimes.ru/post/289965/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==争议==
一些消费者称Denuvo防篡改缩短了[[固态硬盘|固态硬盘]]（SSD）的寿命，因为它将过量的数据写入驱动器<ref name="ASidCast">{{cite web |last1=Kalra |first1=Karan |title=How The New DRM Denuvo Might Be Damaging Your SSD [Update] |url=http://asidcast.com/index.php/2014/11/new-drm-denuvo-might-damaging-ssd |website=ASidCast |publisher=ASidCast |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150119041502/http://asidcast.com/index.php/2014/11/new-drm-denuvo-might-damaging-ssd |archivedate=2015-01-19 |accessdate=2016-02-06 }}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Gründken|first1=Benjamin|title=Dragon Age: Inquisition — Meldungen um SSDs zerstörenden Denuvo-Kopierschutz verunsichern Spieler, viel Lärm um nichts?|url=http://www.pcgameshardware.de/Dragon-Age-Inquisition-PC-236767/News/Dragon-Age-Inquisition-denuvo-drm-zerstoert-angeblich-ssds-1143596/|website=PCGamesHardware.de|publisher=PCGamesHardware|accessdate=2016-02-06|archive-date=2014-11-25|archive-url=https://archive.is/20141125023721/http://www.pcgameshardware.de/Dragon-Age-Inquisition-PC-236767/News/Dragon-Age-Inquisition-denuvo-drm-zerstoert-angeblich-ssds-1143596/|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|last1=Nguyen|first1=The-Khoa|title=Zerstört neuer Denuvo-Kopierschutz SSD-Laufwerke?|url=http://www.pc-magazin.de/news/fifa-15-dragon-age-kopierschutz-denuvo-ssd-laufwerk-kaputt-2733997.html|website=PC Magazin|publisher=PC Magazin|accessdate=2016-02-06|archive-date=2016-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160216222136/http://www.pc-magazin.de/news/fifa-15-dragon-age-kopierschutz-denuvo-ssd-laufwerk-kaputt-2733997.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Denuvo-Kopierschutz zerstört gerüchteweise SSD-Laufwerke|url=http://www.gulli.com/news/25172-denuvo-kopierschutz-zerstoert-geruechteweise-ssd-laufwerke-2014-11-21|website=Gulli.com|publisher=Gulli|accessdate=2016-02-06|archive-date=2014-11-25|archive-url=https://archive.is/20141125023727/http://www.gulli.com/news/25172-denuvo-kopierschutz-zerstoert-geruechteweise-ssd-laufwerke-2014-11-21|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外，也有测试者发现Denuvo影响游戏性能，会延长加载时间和突然掉帧<ref>{{cite news |last1=Machkovech |first1=Sam |title=Evidence continues to mount about how bad Denuvo is for PC gaming performance |url=https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2018/12/evidence-continues-to-mount-about-how-bad-denuvo-is-for-pc-gaming-performance/ |accessdate=2018-12-28 |work=Ars Technica |date=2018-12-26 |language=en-us |archive-date=2019-04-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190410171912/https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2018/12/evidence-continues-to-mount-about-how-bad-denuvo-is-for-pc-gaming-performance/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。 但Denuvo开发商一直声称不会影响游戏<ref name="Denuvo" />。

